transmission and telecom infrastructure business in India. It offers engineering, procurement, and construction services to telecom and power companies. The company also provides turnkey services, including wireless survey, engineering and design, civil works, electrical works, equipment installation and commissioning, as well as operation and maintenance of cell sites both RTT & GBT; wire-line survey, engineering and design, ROW clearance, permissions, laying of duct/cable, jointing, and testing and commissioning, such as fiber and copper; construction of transmission line; and supply of customized LT switch gears, and HT and LT panels comprising lying of cable, terminations, and installation and commissioning. It is involved in ground-mounted solar panel installations; providing solutions for electrical connections, switchgear installations, cable laying, and system integration; and maintenance services. The company was formerly known as Neueon Towers Limited and changed its name to Neueon Corporation Limited in September 2025. Neueon Corporation Limited incorporated in 2006 and is based in Hyderabad, India."}}